&{template:default} {{name=Melee Attack - ClawsOfDarkness}} {{Description=*@{Selected|Character_name} makes a Claws of Darkness attack at a target within 10 feet*}} [[ [[ [[1d10!cf<1cs>10 [Spell Dice]]] [Spell Dice] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Charisma_mod} [Cha]]] [Cha] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Spell=$[[0]] Cold}} {{Dice Mods=$[[1]] varies}} {{Static=$[[3]] Cold + $[[4]] Varies}} {{Dice Total=$[[2]] ***Dice Damage*** }} {{Static Total=$[[6]] ***Static Damage*** }} {{Total=$[[7]] **Total Damage** }}
