ClawsOfDarkness with GreatStrike - Unnested Macros - Works on it's own, but not in a nested query
---------------------------------------------
ClawsOfDarkness-GreatStrike-Cha-Standard
&{template:default} {{name=Great Strike - ClawsOfDarkness}} {{Description=*@{Selected|Character_name} makes a **Great Strike** ClawsOfDarkness attack at a target within 10 feet*}} [[ [[ [[1d10!cf<4cs>10 [Spell Dice]]] [Spell Dice] + [[1d10!cf<0cs>100 [Great Strike]]] [Great Strike] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Charisma_mod} [Cha] ]] [Cha] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Spell=$[[0]] + $[[1]] Cold }}{{Dice Mods=$[[2]] Varies}} {{Static=$[[4]] Cold + $[[5]] Varies}} {{Dice Total=$[[3]] ***Dice Damage*** }} {{Static Total=$[[7]] ***Static Damage*** }} {{Total=$[[8]] **Total Damage** }} {{Slasher Hit= Once per turn when you hit a creature with an attack that deals Cold damage you can reduce the speed of the target by 10 feet until the start of your next turn.}} 
---------------------------------------------
ClawsOfDarkness-GreatStrike-Cha-Advantage
