?{Attack Type?|Standard,%{Selected|ClawsOfDarkness-Slasher-Cha-Standard-Nested} |Advantage,%{Selected|ClawsOfDarkness-Slasher-Cha-Advantage-Nested} |Disadvantage,%{Selected|ClawsOfDarkness-Slasher-Cha-Disadvantage-Nested} |Double Advantage,%{Selected|ClawsOfDarkness-Slasher-Cha-Advantage2-Nested} |Double Disadvantage,%{Selected|ClawsOfDarkness-Slasher-Cha-Disadvantage2-Nested} |Triple Advantage,%{Selected|ClawsOfDarkness-Slasher-Cha-Advantage3-Nested} |Triple Disadvantage,%{Selected|ClawsOfDarkness-Slasher-Cha-Disadvantage3-Nested}} 
---------------------------------------------
