&{template:default&#125; {{name=Great Strike - ClawsOfDarkness (Disadvantage x3)&#125;&#125; {{Description=*@{Selected|Character_name} makes a **Great Strike** ClawsOfDarkness attack at a target within 10 feet at **Triple Disadvantage** *&#125;&#125; [[ [[ [[4d10!!cf<4cs>10kl1 [Spell Dice]]] [Spell Dice] + [[1d10!cf<0cs>100 [Great Strike]]] [Great Strike] + [[@{Selected|global_damage_mod_roll}]] [Global Dice Mods] ]] [Total Dice] + [[ [[@{Selected|Charisma_mod} [Cha] ]] [Cha] + [[1 [Magic Spell]]] [Magic Spell] + [[@{Selected|global_attack_mod}]] [Global Static Mods] ]] [Total Static] ]] {{Spell=$[[0]] + $[[1]] Cold &#125;&#125;{{Dice Mods=$[[2]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Static=$[[4]] + $[[5]] Cold + $[[6]] Varies&#125;&#125; {{Dice Total=$[[3]] ***Dice Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Static Total=$[[8]] ***Static Damage*** &#125;&#125; {{Total=$[[9]] **Total Damage** &#125;&#125; {{Slasher Hit= Once per turn when you hit a creature with an attack that deals Cold damage you can reduce the speed of the target by 10 feet until the start of your next turn.&#125;&#125; {{Slasher Crit=When you score a critical hit that deals Cold damage to a creature you grievously wound it. Until the start of your next turn, the target has disadvantage on all attack rolls.&#125;&#125;
